# Google Analytics 4 Measurement ID (looks like G-XXXXXXXXXX).
# Create a GA4 property at https://analytics.google.com, copy the Measurement ID,
# then set this variable — locally in a .env file, and in Vercel under
# Project Settings → Environment Variables. Rebuild/redeploy after setting it.
# If left unset, Google Analytics is simply disabled (no errors).
VITE_GA_ID=
